comment:
I personally believe that there is way more to the story than we've seen or heard. I am not sure what is going on and furthermore I really could careless. The only thing I have seen this woman in was Aquaman and nothing else, I did not think she even did a reasonably good job, either her acting skills are horrific or the director was not very good, However I believe that her acting skills are lacking. 
 As for Mr. Depp I always liked him in 21 Jump street and even in the first "A Nightmare on Elm St." I enjoyed the Pirates thing. But as for his personal life I know nothing, I do know every time I seen him on tv he was always respectful and polite. It is hard to believe things said about the man. But then again I really do not care either way. I just feel bad for the man to be victimized by a vindictive woman out for something that she does not deserve or entitled to.
 Now as bad as this is going to read, I feel the woman should do time in prison and pay a very hefty fine for her story telling ways. And I mean the maximum no questions asked.
 It is women like this that give other women a bad name and because of that trust has become extinct and no longer exists today.
